Description:
UNDER OFFER
Situated in the popular Mayfield Estate close to schools, shops, transport and sporting facilities, this quality home will make you the envy of all who visit.
With a list of desirable features simply too long to mention, we can only do our best to try and paint a picture.
Boasting a generously sized formal lounge, very well appointed kitchen with stainless steel appliances, dishwasher and walk-in pantry, overlooking your spacious meals/family room, large bedrooms with built-in robes, master with full ensuite and walk-in robe, gas ducted heating throughout, split system air conditioning, and the list goes on.
If you enjoy entertaining then look no further, as this beautiful home comes fully equipped with a covered outdoor entertaining area and low maintenance yard, which leads off from the family room and would be perfect for fun filled days with family and friends all year round.
With everything you could ever want or need in the highest levels of quality family living, this property represents a fantastic opportunity on a corner allotment of 469sqm (approx.).
Inspection we can assure you will not disappoint.
Proudly marketed by Knox's Number 1 Agency
Thinking of selling? Call us today; Boronia office on 9761 2277, Wantirna office on 9800 1225, Rowville office on 9755 6666, Bayswater office on 9720 3030 or Ferntree Gully office on 9752 2889.
TO REGISTER YOUR INTEREST click on either of the following tabs and fill in your details, BOOK AN INSPECTION on the Biggin & Scott website or EMAIL AGENT / CONTACT AGENT on Real Estate.com.au and other websites. You will be contacted by one of our agents and will also receive a text advising of inspection times.

Description:
Win at Tarwin!
Contemporary in its styling, this quality built home comes with an impressive list of inclusions.
Beginning with 4 bedrooms, 2 ensuites and dual open plan living zones there are quite a few clever additions which make this home your family's obvious choice.
The heart of the home with the open plan meals, living space and kitchen with upgraded stainless steel appliances, Bosch dishwasher and multiple and clever storage facilities.
Completing the home are; double car garage, ducted heating, split system, alfresco with gas mains outlet and an impressive solar array.
Premium location in the Hunt Club with both the Cranbourne East Primary and Secondary Schools less than 500 meters away, surrounded by parks, and a host of Casey's best sporting and shopping facilities, this home is brimming with both obvious and salient advantages.
With education, lifestyle, health, recreation, shopping, medical, and transportation hubs nearby
this terrific opportunity will be gone in a flash! Secure your win at Tarwin.
To ensure there is enough demand to inspect the property, please advise us of your wish to attend by simply following these instructions.
- Book inspection
- Select a date and time based on the options displayed
- Enter your details
- Select 'register inspection time'
You're finished! We'll keep you updated if anything changes, but otherwise we look forward to meeting you at our Hodges Open for Inspection.

Description:
Executive Living!
This quality home will satisfy all your desires with its ultra-modern design and excellent location in the popular Parks Edge Estate.
You will love the well designed floorplan which incorporates 3 generous sized bedrooms (master with ensuite & ceiling fan for comfort), study/4th bedroom for the larger families, theatre room, spacious open plan living area with dining area plus a stunning kitchen with walk in pantry, gas cooking, stainless steel appliances and dishwasher. Comfort assured with ducted heating, evaporative cooling and double garage. Outdoor lovers and entertainers will appreciate the decked pergola/BBQ entertaining area.
Cranbourne East is located on the outskirts of Cranbourne Central. The area offers Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College as well as Cranbourne Secondary College and is surrounded by multiple Shopping Centres. Also located nearby is Casey Fields football ground, Casey Race Recreation & Aquatic Centre, and Casey Library.
Welcome to your new home!

Description:
Big Block, Big Home, Big Opportunity
Offering a lifestyle to envy in the heart of the Hunt Club Estate sits this STUNNING family home designed and built by Metricon on a huge 651m2 block. With all the upgrades, meticulous presentation and functional layout - you would be insane to build something new!
Comprising of:
- Master suite with large ensuite including twin vanities and double oversized shower plus a generous WIR.
- 3 further spacious bedrooms all with BIR's.
- Beautiful central kitchen with ample bench and cupboard space, dishwasher and quality appliances. Upgrades include waterfall stone benchtops, 900mm oven with gas cooking, glass splash back and a walk in butler's pantry.
- Two separate living zones to enjoy - a spacious formal lounge/theater room plus a large open plan family area
- For the entertainer's there is a fantastic decked alfresco for the summer BBQ that overlook's the huge backyard.
Added extras include; ducted gas heating, spilt system A/C, down lights throughout, double remote garage with internal access plus LOADS more!
On top of all the amazing features this property has to offer, it is also found in a quiet location and only a stone's throw from Cranbourne East schools and childcare, parks, shopping centers and wetlands. Everything is at your fingertips!
To summarize this amazing home boasts style and distinction at the forefront of design - treat your family to this sophisticated home they will enjoy for years to come!

Description:
Brand new double storey townhouse with view
We are proud to present to you this brand new double-storey townhouse located in the heart of the Livingston Estate, Cranbourne East. You'll join a modern, active and convenient community with amenities such as Casey RACE, Casey Fields sporting facilities and central Cranbourne all at your fingertips!
Boasting 3 generous bedrooms, there's more than ample space for the growing family plus the bonus of two separate bathrooms. The stylish home also offers a light filled open plan living area and an impressive fully equipped kitchen including stainless steel appliances plus fantastic cupboard and bench space. Step outside and you'll find a fabulous alfresco balcony to entertain your guests with a BBQ. Extra features include a split system A/C unit, landscaped gardens, 1 car garage with direct internal access plus a separate undercover car spot, downlights throughout, storage room and more.
Features include:
- 3 Generous bedrooms all with BIR's and electric heaters.
- Large open plan living area opening up to the alfresco balcony.
- Uninterrupted views to Dandenong Ranges
- Two separate bathrooms â one on each level.
- Landscaped front yard with its own street frontage.
- Heating and cooling, downlights.
- Kitchen with plenty of cupboard & bench space, gas cooktop and tiled splashback
- Position perfect: easily within walking distance to a brand new childcare facility, Livingston park and walking tracks as well as the proposed local convenience store and health facilities.
The immaculate property has its own frontage on Elmslie Drive, Cranbourne East located off Eliburn Drive, Cranbourne. Turn right onto Elmslie Drive off Eliburn when coming from Cranbourne- Berwick Road and the frontage for this property will be on the left. For further directions please feel free to contact us.

Description:
BLISSFUL LIVING IN A PRIME LOCATION
CRANBOURNE EAST: Live a lifestyle of comfort in this exquisite home. Built in early 2017 and barely a year old, you will fall in love instantly.
Comprising of 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, double car garage and two separate living areas, there is plenty of space for the whole family. The master bedroom has a full en-suite, with the other three bedrooms being serviced by the second bathroom. The kitchen will also not disappoint with Caesar stone bench tops, 900mm cook top and oven and built in pantry.
Entertaining your family and friends will be easy with the open plan and formal living areas. If you prefer to entertain outdoors, this beautiful home offers a fully landscaped backyard, where you can sit back and relax, with everything taken care of.
Summary of internal and external features include:
- Approx. 435 sqm land & Built in 2017
- Two separate living zones - open plan living and formal lounge
- Plenty of natural light all day
- Master with full en suite with WIR
- Ducted heating
- High ceiling
- Tiled Splash Back
- Caesar stone bench top in Kitchen
- 900 mm oven
- 900 mm gas cook top
- Spacious built in pantry
- Dishwasher
- Overhead cupboards in the kitchen
- Stainless steel range hood
- Solar hot water system
- Remote controlled double lock up garage
- Internal and external access from the garage
- Fully secure and landscaped backyard
Major Amenities nearby:
* Wilandra Rise primary school is few steps away from the house
* Selandra Rise & Pasadena shopping centres are approximately two minutes' drive away from the house
* The Selandra Rise heritage park, Community centre & Kids on Clyde (Child care) centres are few minutes' away from the house
* Bus stop is approximately two minutes' away from the house
* Berwick and Cranbourne railway stations are approximately 15 minutes' drive away either way
* St Thomas the apostle primary school is approximately two minutes' drive away from the house
* St. Peters secondary collage is approximately about a minute drive away from the house
* Casey Fields is approximately five minutes' drive away from the house
* The Casey Complex & Casey RACE are approximately five minutes' drive away from the house

Description:
Stunning family entertainer on 515m2
(HUNT CLUB) --- This outstanding large family home is located within a seconds walk to public transport, parks, lakes, as well as the Cranbourne East School and HUNT CLUB shopping village. Situated on a spacious 515m2 block, the functional floorplan boasts two separate living zones, a beautiful large kitchen and to top it off a fantastic entertainers area outside!
The property consists of 4 large bedrooms all with BIR's - Master including large WIR as well as ensuite. There is plenty of living space to enjoy with a large formal lounge area for guests, as well as a generous family living and family dining area. The well-appointed kitchen includes plenty of bench and cupboard space plus gas cooktop, electric oven, a dishwasher and large built in pantry for storage.
Step outside and you'll find a fantastic decked outdoor area perfect for entertaining a number of family and friends! This is complimented by a spacious rear backyard with plenty of space for kids and pets to play.
The property offers a multitude of extra features which include ducted heating, refrigerated ducted cooling, quality window fittings and fixtures throughout as well as beautifully landscaped gardens.
Comprising of:
- 4 large bedrooms, master with Ensuite & WIR.
- 2 separate living areas.
- Massive decked outdoor area for all your entertaining needs.
- Double lock up garage with rear roller door access.
- Other features include ducted heating, refrigerated ducted cooling, shutter blinds to both bathrooms, solar panels, rainwater tank, garden shed, landscaped gardens and much more.
The property is conveniently located within walking distance to the Hunt Club Wetlands, walking/bicycle paths, childcare, primary and secondary schools, public transport and the new HUNT CLUB SHOPPING VILLAGE â it's got it ALL! To ensure you don't miss out on this amazing opportunity please make sure you contact us to organize an inspection!

Description:
EVERYTHING YOU COULD WANT!
Situated in the highly sort after Cascades on Clyde estate sits this exceptional family home which resides on a huge 548m2 block complete with all the extras and more!
This 4 bedroom delight comes complete with a generous sized master with walk in robes and full en suite including dual vanities.
The hostess kitchen is a chef's dream and is complete with quality stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, 600mm range hood and a 4-burner cook top. Not to mention the island bench with breakfast bar, ample cupboard/storage space and tiled splash back, all this and a whole lot more overlooking the separate over sized meals zone.
Those who like to entertain are bound to enjoy the multitude of separate living zones on offer. This home provides the perfect amount of space to accommodate families and guests of all sizes.
Added extras include: Internal access to your remote double lock up garage, ducted heating & evaporative cooling, down lights, low maintenance front and rear gardens, rear roller door, neutral tones throughout as well as a convenient blend of tiles and carpet throughout.
Step through the sliding doors out to your quality built large scale alfresco with an enormous rear yard; this will provide the perfect setting to entertain all year round!
This is a tremendous opportunity for a family who insists on nothing but the best!
Surrounded by top end properties the location is very appealing and is within walking distance to picturesque wetlands. Other estate features include Class-A recycled water ensuring lush gardens year round, over 14 hectares of parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities, playgrounds and walking tracks. Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne.
Minutes away from Freeway access en route to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre, not to mention walking distance from the Selandra Rise shopping centre and Hunt Club village!
